# ANCHOR / DEV environment = harness deps + the anchor Qiskit wheel.
# This is where Phase 0 (manifest + smoke profile), the unit tests, and the statevector
# feasibility check run -- they all need *a* Qiskit to execute against, and the anchor
# (2.4.2) is the reference build for the study.
#
# This does NOT violate the two-layer model (METHODOLOGY §0.1): the per-event measurements
# in Phase 2 still use Qiskit built FROM SOURCE per event (build_qiskit_event). The anchor
# wheel here is only the development/CI reference.

-r requirements.harness.in
qiskit==2.4.2
qiskit-aer        # oracle simulation (sampled/observable checks); depends on qiskit
